        <div class="row fade-in-section">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="info-block p-3 mb-4">
                    <h4><i class="info-icon fas fa-users"></i>Thousands of Students</h4>
                    <p>Every year, we inspire and educate thousands of high school students in the field of physics and related disciplines. For many of our participants, FYKOS events are what sparked their interest in a scientific career.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
