                <div class="info-block p-3 mb-4">
                    <h4><i class="info-icon fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>Non-Profit</h4>
                    <p>We organize events not for money, but because we believe in their purpose. Participation in all events is either free (often providing financial support for accommodation to increase accessibility) or for a symbolic fee.</p>
                </div>
